### Basic product lookup (Dutch market)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-001?market=nl-NL

### Product with customer-specific pricing (German market, Gold dealer)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-001?market=de-DE&customerId=CUST-GOLD

### Polish market — localized product names
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-002?market=pl-PL

### Silver customer discount
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-001?market=nl-NL&customerId=CUST-SILVER

### Bronze customer discount
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-002?market=de-DE&customerId=CUST-BRONZE

### Unknown product — expects 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/UNKNOWN?market=nl-NL

### Invalid market code — expects 400
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-001?market=invalid

### Missing market parameter — expects 400
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/PRD-001

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
